\begin_layout Paragraph*

\series medium
In this users' guide, we will assume that the reader has a basic familiarity
 with traditional MODE, its internal operation, (convolution thresholding,
 fuzzy logic matching and merging) and its output.
 We will not review these things here.
 Instead, we will point out differences in MTD from the way traditional
 MODE does things when they come up.
 This release is a beta version of MTD, intended mostly to encourage users
 to experiment with it and give us feedback and suggestions to be used in
 a more robust MTD release in the future.
\end_layout

